  <brief_title>Innovative Pulmonary Solutions (IPS) System for Targeted Lung Denervation</brief_title>
  <acronym>IPS-I</acronym>
  <official_title>Evaluation of the Innovative Pulmonary Solutions (IPS) System for Targeted Lung Denervation (TLD) Therapy in Patients With Moderate to Severe Chronic Obstructive Pulmonary Disease (COPD) - A Safety Study</official_title>
