  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to evaluate the safety of Targeted Lung Denervation Therapy (or
      TLD TherapyTM) in patients suffering from COPD. Technical feasibility of the IPS SystemTM
      will also be evaluated through confirmation of successful application of TLD Therapy.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
